Dataset name:
Gravity Recovery and Climate Experiments (GRACE)

Varialbe name: 
lwe_thickness (Liquid Water Equivalent Thickness)

Reference of original data:
Landerer F.W. and S. C. Swenson, Accuracy of scaled GRACE terrestrial water storage estimates. 
         Water Resources Research, Vol 48, W04531, 11 PP, doi:10.1029/2011WR011453 2012.
Swenson, S. C. and J. Wahr, Post-processing removal of correlated errors in GRACE data, 
         Geophys. Res. Lett., 33, L08402, doi:10.1029/2005GL025285, 2006.

Downloaded site:
http://grace.jpl.nasa.gov/data/gracemonthlymassgridsland/

